    {
      "type": "heading",
      "value": "What are Mixins?"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "value": "Mixins are a way to reuse component logic across multiple Vue components by merging shared functionality."
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "value": "Why Use Mixins?"
    },
    {
      "type": "list",
      "value": [
        "**Reuse common logic**",
        "**Reduce code duplication**",
        "**Share functionality across components**",
        "**Simplify maintenance**"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "value": "Basic Example"
    },
    {
      "type": "code",
      "language": "javascript",
      "value": "const myMixin = {\n  data() {\n    return { count: 0 };\n  },\n  methods: {\n    increment() {\n      this.count++;\n    }\n  }\n};"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "value": "Using Mixin"
    },
    {
      "type": "code",
      "language": "javascript",
      "value": "export default {\n  mixins: [myMixin]\n};"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "value": "Merging Behavior"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "value": "Vue merges data, methods, and lifecycle hooks from mixins into components."
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "value": "Lifecycle Hooks in Mixins"
    },
    {
      "type": "code",
      "language": "javascript",
      "value": "const mixin = {\n  mounted() {\n    console.log('Mixin mounted');\n  }\n};"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "value": "Limitations"
    },
    {
      "type": "list",
      "value": [
        "**Name conflicts between mixin and component**",
        "**Hard to trace logic origin**",
        "**Less explicit than composition API**"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "value": "Best Practices"
    },
    {
      "type": "list",
      "value": [
        "**Use mixins for simple reusable logic**",
        "**Avoid large or complex mixins**",
        "**Use Composition API for better clarity**",
        "**Document mixin behavior clearly**"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "value": "Common Mistakes"
    },
    {
